attributes.description: Overview of the Events collected by the Imperva Cloud WAF.

params.markdown:
#### Imperva Cloud WAF

#### Overview

This dashboard visualizes security and access related events collected by Imperva Cloud WAF using the Event Data-stream. It provides metrics for total sites and different types of requests . It also provides an overview of events on the basis of browser type, http status code, request type, country code, action, attack type, client application, URL, User Agent and Source IP.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/imperva_cloud_waf/overview)
